sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Editor as NoteEditor
  participant API as Worker
  participant GH as GitHub_Issues

  User->>Editor: 每键输入
  Editor->>Editor: 立刻更新 textarea（本地）
  Note over Editor: 2s debounce 计时
  User->>Editor: 继续打字则重置计时
  Editor->>API: 停打 2s 后 PATCH
  API->>GH: GET issue（合并 frontmatter）
  API->>GH: PATCH issue
  GH-->>API: updated issue
  API-->>Editor: NoteDetail
  Editor->>Editor: 更新 baseline + 状态栏「已保存」
